s and the cellular industry.<br />\nMikell started his mortgage career in 2007 as an FHA/VA specialist focusing on government sponsored loans and learning the ins and outs of HUD to help his clients from all walks of life the opportunity to buy a home. He understands the broad range of clients needs, from first time home buyers to the refinancing needs of the most seasoned home owners, now he offers a full range of financial mortgage planning. Conventional, Jumbo, VA, FHA, HARP and many other types of other government programs are examples of his professional expertise.<br />\nMikell is passionate about his career and has considerable knowledge about the lending industry and is considered and knowledgeable resource in his company. His work ethic and loyalty have earned him top awards within his company and the industry. Staying active in the community, Mikell serves on the African American Chamber of Commerce as vice chair as he helps to grow the chamber through events, community involvement, and business leadership.<br />\nMikell married his high school sweetheart of 21 years and resided in Cottonwood Heights, Utah. They have two beautiful children, and when he is not with them, you can find him at a local ski resort snowboarding, playing basketball or by a grill entertaining.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" background_color=\"#e8e8e8\" admin_label=\"Section\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_blurb title=\"FAST CREDIT CHECK AND MATCH WITH THE BEST DEALS\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%57%%\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#e02b20\" text_orientation=\"center\" admin_label=\"Blurb\" custom_css_blurb_title=\"margin-bottom: 5%;\" body_font_size=\"16px\" body_line_height=\"1.2em\"]\r\n\r\n<p>Secure and fast soft credit checks that will blow your mind! We can help you as you use our tool, or just contact us and receive help from Mikell.</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_blurb title=\"Get Approved instantly by Uploading your Documents\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%97%%\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#e02b20\" text_orientation=\"center\" admin_label=\"Blurb\" custom_css_blurb_title=\"margin-bottom: 5%;\" body_font_size=\"16px\" body_line_height=\"1.1em\"]\r\n\r\n<p>WHO USES FAX NOW A DAYS RIGHT!? We are up-to-date with new technology and everything can be done online. No need for long processes.</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_blurb title=\"Best rates for Utah residents IN ANY ArEA.\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%134%%\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#e02b20\" text_orientation=\"center\" admin_label=\"Blurb\" custom_css_blurb_title=\"margin-bottom: 5%;\" body_font_size=\"16px\" body_line_height=\"1.1em\"]\r\n\r\n<p>By researching with us you are tapping into a huge database of mortgage information, making it guaranteed for you to have the best deals at all times.</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"Section\"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_blurb title=\"Lern more about the terms we use in the mortgage world\" url=\"/lingo\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%254%%\" icon_color=\"#e02b20\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"center\"][/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"Section\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_contact_form captcha=\"off\" title=\"Contact us now!\" admin_label=\"Contact Form\" module_id=\"et_pb_contact_form_0\"][et_pb_contact_field field_id=\"Name\" field_title=\"Name\"][/et_pb_contact_field][e