e time, guaranteeing that you will receive the best deals.</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Best Support To Find a Home\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%95%%\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#e02b20\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"center\" body_font_size=\"14px\"]\r\n\r\n<p class=\"\">Get the best support to find a place for you with our tool. It is fast and secure, compare prices and do some research without committing to real estate agents, or any mortgage companies.</p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Fast Answer\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%92%%\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#e02b20\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"center\" header_font_size=\"18px\" body_font_size=\"14px\"]\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">As you find a home, and you look to get a mortgage, it is hard to visit and research the best lenders, look up different values, etc. This causes too much time to be wasted. By using our tool you can go through years of research in one click.</span></p>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"Section\" background_color=\"#d1d1d1\" custom_padding=\"0px|0px|0px|0px\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"on\" use_custom_gutter=\"on\" gutter_width=\"1\" custom_padding=\"0px|0px|0px|0px\" parallax_method_1=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_slider admin_label=\"Slider\" auto=\"on\" auto_speed=\"4000\" auto_ignore_hover=\"on\" body_font_size=\"16px\" body_line_height=\"1em\"]\r\n\r\n[et_pb_slide heading=\"Kevin Martin\" background_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0)\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\"]\r\n\r\nWe have used Mikell twice in the last couple of years. He first completed a refinance for us and he was so great to work with that we went right to him when we were purchasing a new home. He is easy to work with and makes the loan process simple. He is very knowledgeable and always walked us through every possible scenario. His knowledge was second to none. He kept us well informed and communicated every step of the way. The thing that we loved most was that Mikell always had our best interest in mind. He never led us in a direction that was contrary to what was best for us. He understood our needs and worked to accomplish our needs without any hidden agenda. I would not hesitate to recommend Mikell to anyone and all of my future business will be done with Mikell.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide heading=\"Don Beck\" background_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0)\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\"]\r\n\r\nThis was a tremendously easy process. Much better than my past experience. Mikell was on top of our processing and made this transaction completely satisfactory. Excellent, excellent, excellent! Great job and we would absolutely recommend Mikell Brown and Christian Roberts Mortgage to anyone seeking financial guidance and mortgage assistance.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide heading=\"Marylynn Beck\" background_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0)\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\"]\r\n\r\nMikell was incredible to work with. We couldnt believe how smooth the refinance process was. He was able to get us a great interest rate that really lowered our monthly mortgage payment. He also assisted us in getting our homeowners insurance, which also resulted in a much lower monthly payment. I will recommend Mikell every chance I get.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_slide]\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_slider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"Section\" background_color=\"#b5b5b5\" custom_padding=\"0px|0px|27px|0px\" global_module=\"395\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" global_parent=\"395\" make_fullwidth=\"on\" use_custom_gutter=\"on\" gutter_width=\"1\" custom_padding=\"27px|0px|27px|0px\" background_color=\"rgba(0,0,0,0.4)\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" parallax_method_3=\"off\" parallax_method_4=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" global_parent=\"395\" text_orientation=\"center\" header_font_size=\"20px\"]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/about-us\"><h1>About us</h1>\r\n\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" global_parent=\"395\" text_orientation=\"center\" header_font_size=\"20px\"]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/mortgage-guide\"><h1>Mortgage Guide</h1></a>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" global_parent=\"395\" text_orientation=\"center\" header_font_size=\"20px\"]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/contact-us\"><h1>Contact Us</h1></a>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" global_parent=\"395\" text_orientation=\"center\" header_font_size=\"20px\"]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/get-started\"><h1>Get Started</h1></a>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" global_parent=\"395\" custom_padding=\"31px|0px|27px|0px\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Image\" global_parent=\"395\" src=\"http://blinkmortgageutah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Christian-Mortgage-Logo.png\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_map admin_label=\"Map\" global_parent=\"395\" address=\"450 300 W, Salt Lake City, UT 84101, USA\" address_lat=\"40.7592399\" address_lng=\"-111.90002809999999\"]\r\n\r\n[et_pb_map_pin title=\"Salt Lake City\" pin_addres